task.summary: Switched primary class from Applet to Panel, removed Coordinate and InputListener.
Uses key bindings instead of KeyListener now.
Added many comments and changed where curves start
Added collision detection with OTHER curves only.
Pressing enter restart the game, escape to exit
Strings are now drawn dynamically such that they're always centered.
ALL strings are now drawn dynamically such that they're always centered.
Command line parameters are now optional
